	(layer "F.Cu")
	(descr "Sansui ST-71 audio transformer, CB-19 LEAD type (リード型). 1P / split secondary 600:600 with center tap. Pads 1,2 = primary (span I=8mm); pads 3,4,5 = secondary (span G=14mm, pitch 7mm) with 4 = center tap. Row spacing C=16.5mm. Body B=20 x A=15.5mm. Flexible ~0.3mm lead wires, drill 0.8mm - hole positions may be adjusted to suit layout. Dimensions from Akizuki Sansui ST datasheet fig.7 (CB-19 lead type).")
